      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Rules engie : If user muted notifications, if balance > $500, if user inactive send PN etc\nPreference : filter notifications based on user preference like 5 notifications a day, dont send notifications in\nquiet hours etc\nnotification template : apply template\nfanout : fanout to different queues\n\nPriority Queues :\n| Priority | Examples   |\n| -------- | ---------- |\n| Critical | OTP, Fraud |\n| High     | Payment    |\n| Medium   | Chat       |\n| Low      | Marketing  |\n\nmulti provider failover",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Rules engie : If user muted notifications, if balance > $500, if user inactive send PN etc\nPreference : filter notifications based on user preference like 5 notifications a day, dont send notifications in\nquiet hours etc\nnotification template : apply template\nfanout : fanout to different queues\n\nPriority Queues :\n| Priority | Examples   |\n| -------- | ---------- |\n| Critical | OTP, Fraud |\n| High     | Payment    |\n| Medium   | Chat       |\n| Low      | Marketing  |\n\nmulti provider failover",
